source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Trigger or query sync

Usage: mxr sync [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --account <ACCOUNT>
          
      --status
          
      --wait
          Wait for the triggered sync to finish before returning. Useful in scripts and CLI smoke tests
      --wait-timeout-secs <WAIT_TIMEOUT_SECS>
          Maximum seconds to wait when --wait is set. Default 60 [default: 60]
      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format. Honored by `--status`; ignored by trigger mode today [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help
          Print help
